        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer76164037" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11188168558635104864">A in-depth biography of a remarkable filly who was born to run. Ruffian is unique in the racing world not only for her speed but for her heart and will to win. She is buried entire near the flagpole at Belmont Park, facing the finish line. Ruffian lived a life of triumph, courage and tragedy, one of the foremost race horses of the 20th century.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


