        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer152431361" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1830960862884046174">Even though I ws a little girl when her tragedy occurred, &amp; knew what the outcome would be before I ever read it, this was an amazing book. It made me laugh, it made me cry. The photos were a wonderful memory to have of this filly who gave her heart to her sport, &amp; who&apos;s broken life touched America&apos;s horse lovers &amp; Thoroughbred lovers around the world. Rest In Peace brave girl. You were a star that burned out way too soon.</span>
