        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/558994117?book_show_action=true">Mar 12, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="L.M. Ransom" class="user" itemprop="url" name="L.M. Ransom" href="/user/show/909411-l-m-ransom">L.M. Ransom</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/909411-l-m-ransom?shelf=horses-n-ponies">horses-n-ponies</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer558994117" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1415340049058232782">Broke my heart. I cried several times during this book (during anything about Ruffian, really), but it&apos;s one of the very BEST horse books I&apos;ve ever read. She was an amazing filly, and it&apos;s a shame she was never able to race again.<br/><br/>If you love horses, please read it. It will break you, but the pain is worthwhile.</span>
  <span id="freeText1415340049058232782" style="display:none">Broke my heart. I cried several times during this book (during anything about Ruffian, really), but it's one of the very BEST horse books I've ever read. She was an amazing filly, and it's a shame she was never able to race again.<br /><br />If you love horses, please read it. It will break you, but the pain is worthwhile.</span>
