<span id="freeTextContainer15984183884059519821">Jane Schwartz has written for many publications, including the <i>New York Times, Sports Illustrated</i>, the <i>Blood-Horse</i>, and <i>Daily Racing Forum</i>, where her column &quot;Free Rein&quot; appeared. She is also the author of a novel. She lives in Brooklyn, New York.</span>
